{% extends "layout.njk" %}

{% block title %}About - Gerudo{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<section class="content-wrapper">
  <h2>About Gerudo</h2>
  
  <div class="card mt-lg">
    <h3 style="color: var(--sage);">What is Gerudo?</h3>
    <p>
      Gerudo is a free web hosting platform inspired by Neocities. It provides a simple, 
      accessible way for anyone to create and publish their own websites without requiring 
      advanced technical knowledge.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="card mt-lg">
    <h3 style="color: var(--sage);">Philosophy</h3>
    <p>
      We believe the web should be a place for creativity, learning, and personal expression. 
      Gerudo aims to capture the spirit of the early web while incorporating modern security 
      and usability practices.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-md">
      This platform is built entirely without client-side JavaScript, demonstrating that 
      modern web applications can be:
    </p>
    <ul style="margin-left: 2rem; margin-top: 0.5rem;">
      <li>Accessible to all users</li>
      <li>Fast and lightweight</li>
      <li>Privacy-respecting</li>
      <li>Functional without JavaScript</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="card mt-lg">
    <h3 style="color: var(--sage);">Features</h3>
    <ul style="margin-left: 2rem; margin-top: 0.5rem;">
      <li><strong>Free Hosting:</strong> Create and host multiple websites at no cost</li>
      <li><strong>Simple Interface:</strong> Easy-to-use dashboard for managing your sites</li>
      <li><strong>Full Control:</strong> Upload HTML, CSS, and JavaScript files</li>
      <li><strong>Community:</strong> Browse and discover sites created by others</li>
      <li><strong>Secure:</strong> Modern security practices protect your data</li>
      <li><strong>No Ads:</strong> Clean, ad-free experience</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="card mt-lg">
    <h3 style="color: var(--sage);">Technology Stack</h3>
    <p>Gerudo is built with:</p>
    <ul style="margin-left: 2rem; margin-top: 0.5rem;">
      <li><strong>Backend:</strong> Node.js + Express</li>
      <li><strong>Database:</strong> PostgreSQL</li>
      <li><strong>Templates:</strong> Nunjucks</li>
      <li><strong>Security:</strong> bcrypt, Helmet, custom anti-DDoS (Zant Gateway)</li>
      <li><strong>Philosophy:</strong> Progressive enhancement, no client-side JS</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="card mt-lg">
    <h3 style="color: var(--sage);">Getting Started</h3>
    <p>Ready to create your first website?</p>
    <div class="flex-center gap-md mt-md">
      {% if not user %}
        <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-primary">Sign Up</a>
        <a href="/browse" class="btn btn-secondary">Browse Sites</a>
      {% else %}
        <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-primary">Go to Dashboard</a>
        <a href="/browse" class="btn btn-secondary">Browse Sites</a>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="text-center mt-xl">
    <p class="text-muted">
      Questions or feedback? Feel free to reach out!
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
{% endblock %}
